in casting the veto us ambassador herbert s okun said the 
resolutions broad and sweeping condemnation of israel contains 
not a scintilla of balance it contains no appeal or request for 
calm 
the measure urged israel to halt deportations condemned human 
rights violations in the occupied territories and called for a 
unsponsored settlement of the arabisraeli conflict 
israel deported eight palestinian civilians earlier this week 
and issued deportation orders for 12 others as part of its effort 
to quell four months of violence in the west bank and gaza that has 
claimed more than 140 arab lives two israelis have died 
