legislation against the takeover and to call for investigations 
cohill said this is a difficult case made all the more 
complex by shearsons quite novel role as 
brokerdealerinvestment bankeradviserowner 
the facts are intricate and complicated the law is fuzzy 
he said 
cohill also said beazers plans to borrow 864 million from a 
bank syndicate led by citibank likely violate federal reserve board 
rules about posting stock as collateral on loans used to buy the 
stock 
the order is the second against the tender offer in a federal 
court 
a judge in los angeles has blocked it on antitrust grounds the 
us 9th circuirt court of appeals will hear arguments may 13 on 
beazers attempt to overturn the los angeles ruling 
beazers plans to sell koppers chemical operations stoked fears 
of losing 1100 jobs in pittsburgh and cohill said the takeover 
should be halted for now because the potential ramifications 
to the pittsburgh community are uncertain and possibly adverse 
in a countersuit the beazer group said kopperss filings in 
response to the tender offer also violated securities laws but 
cohill said the tender offer apparently is invalid under federal 
securities laws and until a valid tender offer is made 
koppers is not obligated to file the proper disclosures 
